<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>

    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>로그인 웹페이지</title>

    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="/css/animate.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">

</head>

<body class="gray-bg">

    <div class="middle-box text-center loginscreen animated fadeInDown">
        <div>
            <h3>관리자 웹사이트에 오신걸 환영합니다.</h3>
            <p>관리자 계정과 암호를 입력해주세요</p>
            <form class="m-t" role="form" action="/login" method="post">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Username" required="" name="admin_id">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="password" name="admin_password" class="form-control" placeholder="Password" required="">
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary block full-width m-b">로그인</button>
            </form>
            <p class="m-t"> <small>Inspinia we app framework base on Bootstrap 3 &copy; 2014</small> </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mainly scripts -->
    <script src="/js/jquery-3.1.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/bootstrap.js"></script>

    <script>
        var loginResultCode = '<%=resultMsg.code%>';

        if(loginResultCode == 401 || loginResultCode == 402) {
            alert("<%=resultMsg.msg%>");
        }
    </script>

</body>

</html>
